they’ve become its prey.

45
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:07,400
The two existing Death Gods
fought hard with it.

46
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:10,750
Only eight people have passed over the past 1000 years.

47
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:14,680
I wonder whether
Asura King and Emissary of Hell can succeed?

48
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:33,840
Let’s go.

49
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,780
Do you want to rest for a few more minutes?

50
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:50,170
It’s hot.

51
00:03:50,170 --> 00:03:53,880
I can feel my energy draining off.

52
00:03:56,090 --> 00:03:57,740
<i>Blue Silver Domain.</i>

53
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:16,200
<i>It has cooled down.</i>

54
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:19,310
<i>Tang Yin’s innate domain enables him</i>

55
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:21,450
<i>to maintain full combat strength
under any circumstances.</i>

56
00:04:21,450 --> 00:04:24,520
<i>Hao Tian Tribe is really
a great place for nurturing talents.</i>

57
00:05:03,230 --> 00:05:04,940
Tang Yin...

58
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:08,720
I’m fine.

59
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,520
Serpent?

60
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:21,930
Watch out. The red maze must be poisonous.

61
00:05:21,930 --> 00:05:24,860
Are we able to dodge on this narrow path?

62
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:26,650
Tang Yin, what shall we do?

63
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,840
The sound, form, and poisonous fire.

64
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,720
Could it be the ancient beast,

65
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,380
Ten-Headed Burning Sun Serpent?

66
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:36,520
There’re nine crystals
glowing with reddish radiance.

67
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,410
Perhaps these are its weakness.

68
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:48,510
This smell... It’s alcohol.

69
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:52,570
<i>As long as it’s snake venom,
it can be suppressed by realgar.</i>

70
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:01,130
The venomous flame is approaching.

71
00:06:10,350 --> 00:06:12,750
<i>It’s incredible to resist the fire with wind,</i>

72
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,680
<i>and yet he seems so calm.</i>

73
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:17,100
I’ll divert its attention,
and you wait for a chance to attack.

74
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,650
Soul bone skill.

75
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:24,250
Coquettish Genie.

76
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,000
I can’t pierce through it.

77
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,390
The flowing flame is like an impregnable armor.

78
00:07:06,090 --> 00:07:09,450
Forty-two, forty-three,

79
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:14,860
forty-four, forty-five...

80
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,150
There’s a flaw here.

81
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:35,560
Watch out!

82
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,820
Seven more to go.

83
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:59,120
Destroy all of them when it’s off-guard.

84
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,480
Your Holiness,

85
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:23,710
Xie Yue and Yan will be back
from Death Valley today.

86
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:25,600
It has been two years.

87
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,880
Have they made any progress?

88
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:33,290
Your Holiness, both of them
are approaching the Level 60.

89
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,710
Great.

90
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:40,200
I’ll send someone to fetch them.

91
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:45,210
Gui Mei, Yue Guan.
Your destination is Slaughter City.

92
00:08:45,210 --> 00:08:46,880
Yes.

93
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:02,980
<i>You must come back alive.</i>

94
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:39,080
[Soul Land]

95
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:44,040
Three left.

96
00:10:44,050 --> 00:10:45,330
Carry on.

97
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,940
<i>It’s neidan.</i>

98
00:10:54,970 --> 00:10:57,470
Oh, no. It’s going to bring us down with it.

99
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:07,050
The pressure is strong.
Don’t we have other alternatives?

100
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:14,400
Darn it.

101
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:29,410
So powerful!

102
00:11:42,830 --> 00:11:44,080
Tang Yin!

103
00:11:55,370 --> 00:12:00,220
The powerful neidan of the serpent
turns the earth pale.

104
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:03,610
I almost lost my life there.

105
00:12:23,070 --> 00:12:26,910
Little San, how would you handle this?

106
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:29,440
<i>If the connection between
the body and the neidan is cut off,</i>

107
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,760
<i>- we still have a chance.</i>
- Tang Yin, you will die for it!

108
00:13:00,270 --> 00:13:06,060
Skill of Random Hammering.

109
00:13:09,850 --> 00:13:15,680
Nine by Nine Consolidate to One.

110
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:39,840
<i>This neidan can invalidate any venom,</i>

111
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,820
<i>and restrain all snakes as well.</i>

112
00:13:46,540 --> 00:13:48,090
Tang Yin!

113
00:13:49,070 --> 00:13:50,200
What’s wrong with you?

114
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:56,380
<i>Blue Silver Domain.</i>

115
00:13:56,750 --> 00:14:00,320
The longer we stay, the harder
we can control the inner heinous spirit.

116
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:09,320
Dash for it.

117
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:21,560
Calm down. Let’s speed up and walk through this.

118
00:14:22,940 --> 00:14:28,520
Tang Yin, I can’t make it.

119
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:39,640
Just hang in there. If I’m not wrong,

120
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,420
