121
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,010
Calm down.

122
00:15:05,530 --> 00:15:09,120
Will they be like the two people before?

123
00:15:11,260 --> 00:15:12,010
[You’ve harmed me.]

124
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:16,640
Kill or to be killed,

125
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:21,790
