126
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,400
Calm yourself.

127
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:40,940
<i>Too bad. If Hu Liena goes ballistic,</i>

128
00:15:40,940 --> 00:15:42,940
<i>she’ll attack me.</i>

129
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:45,740
<i>I might win if I resist with all force,</i>

130
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:50,160
<i>but I’ll be injured instead.
Is killing her the only way?</i>

131
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:05,610
Tang Yin, I can’t resist anymore.

132
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:08,020
Insensate me before I go ballistic.

133
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:10,220
Please bring me out.

134
00:16:10,730 --> 00:16:13,260
Hurry up. Do it.

135
00:16:23,310 --> 00:16:26,140
<i>Even Hu Liena can’t stick to the end.</i>

136
00:16:26,170 --> 00:16:28,620
<i>So, the most threatening obstacle here
is not from the external,</i>

137
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:30,620
<i>but the evil in our heart.</i>

138
00:16:32,190 --> 00:16:36,060
<i>Luckily, I have Blue Silver Domain
and Wisdom Skull.</i>

139
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,490
<i>The base of Slaughter City</i>

140
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:42,720
<i>is Yomigaeri, formed by the mixture
of degenerates’ souls and toxins.</i>

141
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:44,480
Although I can’t resolve it,

142
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:46,120
