143
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:52,560
<i>This Bloody Swan Kiss</i>

144
00:16:52,570 --> 00:16:54,440
<i>will stimulate the toxins by many folds,</i>

145
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:59,210
<i>strong enough to make Yomigaeri
a venomous toxins without antidote.</i>

146
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:21,250
<i>Slaughter City, Slaughter King,</i>

147
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:24,510
<i>I hope you’ll like my present.</i>

